high_descs: Turn to your right then walk straight, turn right facing the counter top beside the microwave
Pick up the knife on the counter top
Turn to your right move few steps then turn left on the stove
Put the knife in the pan on the stove
Pick up the pan with knife
Turn to your right then head to counter top beside the right side of the sink
Put the pan with knife on the right side of the sink at the counter top
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with knife on the counter top beside the sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn right and walk towards the counter, then turn left to face the stove.
Put the butter knife in the pan that is on the front right burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal pan with the butter knife in it off of the stove.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Put the pan with the butter knife in it on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, proceed to end of counter, turn right.
Pick up knife from counter, located to the left of the egg.
Turn right, turn left to face stove.
Put knife in pan on bottom right burner.
Pick up pan with knife in it.
Turn around, proceed to sink.  Turn left to face sink.
Put pan with knife in it to the right of the sink on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put knife in pan, move both to counter by sink.
